<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-01-0958 </DOCNO><TEXT>We described a high pressure reactive dc-sputtering system for a-Si:Hdeposition. Optical and electrical transport measurement were performedin order to characterize the films. Results of dark and photoconductivityas a function of temperature and hydrogen content, and optical gap dependenceon hydrogen content are present. (M.W.O.).</TEXT></DOC>